Regulation Name(s): Quality control material, assayed and unassayed
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Elecsys CA 125 II CalCheck 5 assayed control for calibration verification on Elecsys and cobas e analyzers
Indications for Use Summary: Assayed control for use in calibration verification and verification of the assay range established by the Elecsys CA 125 II reagent on Elecsys and cobas e immunoassay analyzers, for in vitro diagnostic use only.
